# IOUSBInterfaceDescriptor

## Declaration

```swift
struct IOUSBInterfaceDescriptor {
   UInt8 bLength;
   UInt8 bDescriptorType;
   UInt8 bInterfaceNumber;
   UInt8 bAlternateSetting;
   UInt8 bNumEndpoints;
   UInt8 bInterfaceClass;
   UInt8 bInterfaceSubClass;
   UInt8 bInterfaceProtocol;
   UInt8 iInterface;
};
```

## Overview

Descriptor for a USB Interface. See the USB Specification at [link-1670329].

## Related Documentation

- **IOUSBInterfaceDescriptor**: A descriptor for a specific interface of a USB device.
